text: Natalia Barbu (born 22 August 1979) is a Moldovan singer and songwriter. She represented Moldova at the Eurovision Song Contest 2007 with the song "Fight", which placed in the top ten at the Grand Final. She represented Moldova again at Eurovision 2024 with the song "In The Middle". == Sources == Category:1979 births Category:Eurovision Song Contest entrants Category:Living people Category:Moldovan singers
